    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You can inspire extreme revulsion when you slaughter your enemies.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Intimidating Prowess, Killing Flourish, Intimidate 11 ranks, slayer level 11th.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Creatures you demoralize by using the Killing Flourish feat must succeed at a Fortitude save (DC = 10 + 1/2 your character level + the higher of your Strength or Dexterity modif ier) or become sickened for 1 minute.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When using this feat, you can spend up to 5 stamina points to increase the DC of the effect by an amount equal to the number of stamina points you spent.",
